albino (COCA 12k) I ended up living with this albino guy who was cleaning windshields&hellip;
The word &ldquo;albino&rdquo; refers to a person or animal with a condition called albinism, which is characterized by a lack of pigment in the skin, hair, and eyes. This results in very light skin, white or pale hair, and eyes that can appear pink or blue due to the visibility of blood vessels.
